query - Query records with filters (compact output)

Usage:
  query <model> [where <conditions>] [order <field> [asc|desc]] [limit <n>]

Operators:
  field=value     Exact match
  field!=value    Not equal
  field>value     Greater than
  field>=value    Greater than or equal
  field<value     Less than
  field<=value    Less than or equal
  field~value     Pattern match (case-insensitive, auto-wildcards)

Examples:
  query users
  query users limit 5
  query users where access=root
  query users where name~john order name limit 10
  query products where price>100 order price desc

Output is compact toon format, optimized for token efficiency.
